00:00:51.799 --> 00:00:54.079
All those noble ladies I found for him

00:00:54.079 --> 00:00:55.520
Which one's family background and upbringing

00:00:55.520 --> 00:00:57.439
And wealth isn't better than this...

00:00:57.439 --> 00:00:58.520
this...

00:00:58.520 --> 00:00:59.920
this serf?

00:00:59.920 --> 00:01:01.479
They're a hundred times better!

00:01:01.479 --> 00:01:02.960
Your words are somewhat inappropriate,

00:01:03.560 --> 00:01:04.680
Lord Balu.

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:07.200
As a former hereditary household serf of Balu Manor,

00:01:07.359 --> 00:01:08.439
and Deji's older sister,

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:10.359
at first,

00:01:10.359 --> 00:01:12.000
I also didn't agree to them being together.

00:01:12.599 --> 00:01:14.239
Since you know

00:01:14.239 --> 00:01:15.640
their statuses are different,

00:01:16.319 --> 00:01:17.079
just like

00:01:17.079 --> 00:01:18.959
yak butter and raw water,

00:01:19.319 --> 00:01:21.000
even if forced together,

00:01:21.040 --> 00:01:21.799
in the end,

00:01:21.799 --> 00:01:22.959
they will still separate.

00:01:23.519 --> 00:01:25.040
If you understand this principle,

00:01:25.200 --> 00:01:26.239
then go

00:01:26.239 --> 00:01:27.359
and persuade him more.

00:01:27.359 --> 00:01:27.959
Ah.

00:01:29.200 --> 00:01:30.000
Yes.

00:01:31.239 --> 00:01:32.040
I understand.

00:01:34.359 --> 00:01:35.920
What I understand is

00:01:36.239 --> 00:01:38.200
the arrogance of noble lords,

00:01:38.200 --> 00:01:39.959
carved into their very bones.

00:01:40.519 --> 00:01:42.599
It's like the walls of this manor,

00:01:43.040 --> 00:01:44.159
so high and thick.

00:01:44.920 --> 00:01:46.159
I understand

00:01:46.159 --> 00:01:47.359
that in your eyes,

00:01:48.200 --> 00:01:50.719
we serfs' bloodlines are inherently lowly.

00:01:51.239 --> 00:01:52.920
Even the air we breathe

00:01:52.920 --> 00:01:54.719
isn't worthy of being as sweet as yours.

00:01:55.599 --> 00:01:56.599
My disagreement

00:01:57.040 --> 00:01:59.319
is precisely because I know too well

00:01:59.319 --> 00:02:00.840
how a lord like you

00:02:01.599 --> 00:02:03.319
would view Deji,

00:02:03.840 --> 00:02:05.439
and how you would view this love.

00:02:06.560 --> 00:02:08.560
Just as you say now:

00:02:08.560 --> 00:02:09.800
"Lowly."

00:02:09.800 --> 00:02:10.560
"Bewitched."

00:02:11.159 --> 00:02:12.560
Using such words

00:02:12.560 --> 00:02:14.719
to tarnish two pure hearts.

00:02:15.319 --> 00:02:16.199
What I feared was

00:02:16.199 --> 00:02:17.439
Deji having to bear

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:20.080
precisely the kind of

00:02:20.080 --> 00:02:21.639
erupting,

00:02:21.919 --> 00:02:23.960
deep-rooted contempt like yours.

00:02:24.240 --> 00:02:25.039
You,

00:02:26.840 --> 00:02:27.919
Zhuoma...

00:02:27.919 --> 00:02:31.159
Perhaps what I'm guarding isn't glory,

00:02:31.159 --> 00:02:35.319
but an old castle long overdue to collapse.

00:02:35.319 --> 00:02:38.479
What a sharp-tongued captain you are.

00:02:39.039 --> 00:02:40.919
So later,

00:02:40.919 --> 00:02:42.319
why did you agree?

00:02:43.639 --> 00:02:45.159
Because I saw rebellion.

00:02:46.479 --> 00:02:49.319
I rebelled against the shackles passed down through serf generations.

00:02:49.520 --> 00:02:50.840
And your son,

00:02:51.080 --> 00:02:52.280
he is rebelling against

00:02:52.280 --> 00:02:53.560
the shackles you imposed on him—

00:02:53.560 --> 00:02:55.960
the shackles of a rigid social hierarchy.

00:02:56.159 --> 00:02:57.120
He rebels against a fate

00:02:57.120 --> 00:02:59.240
that forbids loving someone you truly love.

00:02:59.520 --> 00:03:01.639
I imposed on him?

00:03:01.639 --> 00:03:03.039
A rigid social hierarchy

00:03:03.159 --> 00:03:04.400
is a rule of our Tibetan people

00:03:04.400 --> 00:03:06.120
for thousands of years!

00:03:07.560 --> 00:03:08.360
Meiduo,

00:03:09.080 --> 00:03:10.840
I can overlook your escape.

00:03:11.360 --> 00:03:13.360
I can even call you Captain.

00:03:13.879 --> 00:03:14.960
I can even

00:03:14.960 --> 00:03:16.879
support your reforms.

00:03:17.039 --> 00:03:18.840
But,

00:03:18.840 --> 00:03:21.159
to accept a serf

00:03:21.159 --> 00:03:22.360
as my daughter-in-law?

00:03:23.159 --> 00:03:24.319
Absolutely not!

00:03:30.240 --> 00:03:32.759
You're not just afraid of the girl Deji.

00:03:33.759 --> 00:03:35.840
What you fear more is

00:03:35.840 --> 00:03:37.319
a new Xizang where serfs' children

00:03:37.879 --> 00:03:39.639
and lords' children

00:03:39.639 --> 00:03:41.919
sit as equals.

00:03:44.560 --> 00:03:46.560
And your most precious son, Yundan,

00:03:47.439 --> 00:03:49.439
has already embraced this new world.

00:03:50.560 --> 00:03:51.840
He chose Deji

00:03:52.319 --> 00:03:53.639
not because he was bewitched,

00:03:54.360 --> 00:03:56.840
but because he saw the rot of the old system.

00:03:57.240 --> 00:03:59.439
He saw the life and partner he truly wants.

00:04:00.639 --> 00:04:02.240
He is rebelling against

00:04:02.240 --> 00:04:04.479
the noble shackles you forced upon him.

00:04:05.039 --> 00:04:06.759
And I rebelled against

00:04:06.759 --> 00:04:07.960
the chains of serfdom.

00:04:08.719 --> 00:04:09.759
In this sense,

00:04:10.479 --> 00:04:12.360
he and I

00:04:12.360 --> 00:04:13.759
are on the same front line.

00:04:15.639 --> 00:04:16.560
Lord!

00:04:16.560 --> 00:04:17.759
Wake up!

00:04:18.079 --> 00:04:18.920
These words

00:04:18.920 --> 00:04:19.959
are all poison!

00:04:20.160 --> 00:04:21.600
They're the bewitching potion

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:23.160
the Han people fed to the Young Master!

00:04:23.560 --> 00:04:26.040
Gesang Meiduo has returned for revenge!

00:04:26.319 --> 00:04:27.839
You must not believe her!

00:04:27.920 --> 00:04:29.839
She is a hereditary household serf,

00:04:29.839 --> 00:04:30.639
a...

00:04:42.680 --> 00:04:44.560
It's not them who are wrong.

00:04:45.839 --> 00:04:47.839
The one who is wrong...

00:04:47.839 --> 00:04:49.360
is me.

00:04:50.480 --> 00:04:51.279
Wangjiu.

00:04:52.439 --> 00:04:54.720
From today onward,

00:04:55.120 --> 00:04:56.639
you are no longer

00:04:56.639 --> 00:04:58.279
the steward of our household.

00:04:58.439 --> 00:04:59.560
You are free.

00:04:59.639 --> 00:05:00.759
Lord...

00:05:09.360 --> 00:05:11.720
Go.

00:05:13.639 --> 00:05:14.439
Yes.

00:05:48.120 --> 00:05:50.959
Tea should be drunk while hot.

00:05:51.959 --> 00:05:54.120
Once it cools,

00:05:54.120 --> 00:05:56.120
the flavor changes.

00:06:00.839 --> 00:06:01.759
Zhuoma,

00:06:03.480 --> 00:06:04.759
my White Tara...

00:06:05.959 --> 00:06:07.680
You watch from the heavens.

00:06:08.360 --> 00:06:09.519
Your eyes

00:06:10.920 --> 00:06:12.120
are always so bright,

00:06:13.519 --> 00:06:14.920
able to see through people's hearts.

00:06:16.920 --> 00:06:18.120
This world...

00:06:19.079 --> 00:06:20.480
has truly changed.

00:06:22.680 --> 00:06:25.399
This old bones of mine

00:06:25.399 --> 00:06:27.120
can't quite keep up.

00:06:28.279 --> 00:06:30.480
Nowadays,

00:06:30.480 --> 00:06:32.240
I can't even intimidate him anymore.

00:06:33.839 --> 00:06:35.360
But what I can do

00:06:37.040 --> 00:06:37.839
is

00:06:39.360 --> 00:06:40.560
to not be the rope

00:06:40.560 --> 00:06:43.160
that ties his wings.

00:06:48.560 --> 00:06:51.000
May Yundan's heart,

00:06:51.000 --> 00:06:53.360
like a stream from melting snow mountains,

00:06:54.360 --> 00:06:56.319
flow steadfastly towards Deji.

00:06:58.120 --> 00:06:59.160
He even

00:06:59.160 --> 00:07:00.680
rebelled for her sake.

00:07:03.360 --> 00:07:05.360
Alright.

00:07:07.040 --> 00:07:08.160
Let us bless them.

00:07:09.560 --> 00:07:10.639
Bless them.

00:07:11.959 --> 00:07:14.240
Bless them

00:07:14.240 --> 00:07:19.519
with peace and happiness.

00:07:40.519 --> 00:07:42.120
I have passed through

00:07:42.120 --> 00:07:43.519
the gates of hell countless times.

00:07:44.519 --> 00:07:46.160
It has trapped countless serfs.

00:07:47.160 --> 00:07:48.279
But I believe

00:07:48.639 --> 00:07:49.639
that one day,

00:07:49.759 --> 00:07:52.879
the shacks on this land will become warm houses,

00:07:54.040 --> 00:07:55.399
and the lord's manor

00:07:55.399 --> 00:07:57.519
will become our shared home.

00:07:59.120 --> 00:08:00.959
If sunlight can reach the cattle sheds,

00:08:01.519 --> 00:08:03.759
if every person bound by chains

00:08:03.959 --> 00:08:05.839
can truly be reborn,

00:08:07.079 --> 00:08:08.600
then this is the ideal

00:08:08.600 --> 00:08:10.720
I would fight with my life

00:08:10.720 --> 00:08:12.120
to achieve.